        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Recalled Veterans Protection Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill exempts members of the Armed Forces who voluntarily separate from active duty and incur a service-connected disability after being recalled to active duty or full-time National Guard duty from the requirement to repay voluntary separation pay.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
